name: 斯凯勒·杜恩
birth_place: 美国,康涅狄格州,布兰福德
introduction: Skylar Dunn took a love for acting at a young age when she began performing as a competitive dancer and in local community theatre. She soon began auditioning and was hooked on playing out the characters of all very different and exciting roles. When Skylar is not acting she loves competitive dance, theatre, football, reading, lacrosse, singing and playing her guitar. Skylar is represented by Don Buchwald and Associates.
